      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a> * Search Explosion</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1883_eruption_of_Krakatoa\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f4/The_Scream.jpg/330px-The_Scream.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"382\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f4/The_Scream.jpg/500px-The_Scream.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f4/The_Scream.jpg/960px-The_Scream.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:The_Scream.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/Category:Edvard_Munch\" title=\"Category:Edvard Munch\">Edvard Munch</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Scream\">The Scream</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p>A <b>Search Explosion</b> or node count explosion refers to a huge <a href=\"/Branching_Factor#EffectiveBranchingFactor\" title=\"Branching Factor\">effective branching factor</a> in <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">iterative deepening</a>, most often caused by <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">move ordering</a> suddenly becomes worse due to new refutations found at higher depth, by re-searching the <a href=\"/Root\" title=\"Root\">root</a> after <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">aspiration window</a> <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">fail-high</a> or <a href=\"/Fail-Low\" title=\"Fail-Low\">fail-low</a>, and/or enabling too many <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">extensions</a> and <a href=\"/Check\" title=\"Check\">checks</a> in <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">quiescence search</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Leonid.27s_Positions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Leonid's Positions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Search_Explosion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mate_Threat_Extensions\" title=\"Mate Threat Extensions\">Mate Threat Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Odd-Even_Effect\" title=\"Odd-Even Effect\">Odd-Even Effect</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Search_Instability\" title=\"Search Instability\">Search Instability</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a></li></ul>\n<p><span id=\"leonid\"></span>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Leonid.27s_Positions\">Leonid's Positions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Search_Explosion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Leonid&#039;s Positions\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><a href=\"/Test-Positions#Leonid\" title=\"Test-Positions\">Chess positions</a> posted by <a href=\"/Leonid_Liberman\" title=\"Leonid Liberman\">Leonid Liberman</a> in <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a> let many engines \"explode\" <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<table class=\"fentt\" style=\"font-size:24pt\"><tr><td class=\"board\" style=\"width: 8em;\"><div class=\"board\"><div class=\"sq\">    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/></div><div class=\"pcbg\">     <br/>    <br/>    <br/>    <br/>   <br/>      <br/>    <br/>     <br/></div><div class=\"pcfg\">♛  ♚  ♛ <br/>  ♞♛♞  ♝<br/> ♞ ♙ ♞ ♝<br/>  ♜♞♜  ♕<br/> ♘♕ ♕♘ ♕<br/>   ♕   ♗<br/>  ♖♕♖  ♗<br/>♕  ♔  ♕ <br/></div></div></td></tr></table> \n<p>q2k2q1/2nqn2b/1n1P1n1b/2rnr2Q/1NQ1QN1Q/3Q3B/2RQR2B/Q2K2Q1 w - - <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Search_Explosion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Search_Explosion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=206721\">Explosion in WAC 102</a> by <a href=\"/David_Rasmussen\" title=\"David Rasmussen\">David Rasmussen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=206802\">No explosions</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_Gemuh\" title=\"Matthias Gemuh\">Matthias Gemuh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=231056\">Threat Extension and Tree Explosion</a> by <a href=\"/Steve_Maughan\" title=\"Steve Maughan\">Steve Maughan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 23, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=267486\">Quiescence Explosion</a> by <a href=\"/David_Rasmussen\" title=\"David Rasmussen\">David Rasmussen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 26, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=267592\">More Explosion</a> by <a href=\"/David_Rasmussen\" title=\"David Rasmussen\">David Rasmussen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 26, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=303257\">Quiescent Explosion</a> by macaroni, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 26, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=344566\">quiesce node explosion</a> by Mike Siler, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=358170\">check extention explosion</a> by Aivaras Juzvikas, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 03, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=444261\">node explosion</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Dahlem&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"David Dahlem (page does not exist)\">David Dahlem</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 22, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=447270\">Node count explosion</a> by <a href=\"/Mridul_Muralidharan\" title=\"Mridul Muralidharan\">Mridul Muralidharan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 03, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=20727\">Quiescence Search Explosions</a> by <a href=\"/Mike_Leany\" title=\"Mike Leany\">Mike Leany</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 18, 2008 </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Search_Explosion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31505\">Problem with exploding tree because of extensions</a> by <a href=\"/Oliver_Brausch\" title=\"Oliver Brausch\">Oliver Brausch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32148\">Avoiding qsearch explosion</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Costalba\" title=\"Marco Costalba\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 29, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2984\">Quiescence node explosion</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Sander_Maassen_vd_Brink&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Sander Maassen vd Brink (page does not exist)\">sandermvdb</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, June 01, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63590\">Q search explosion</a> by <a href=\"/Colin_Jenkins\" title=\"Colin Jenkins\">Colin Jenkins</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 30, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Search_Explosion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74345\">search explosion</a> by <a href=\"/Vivien_Clauzon\" title=\"Vivien Clauzon\">Vivien Clauzon</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 02, 2020</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Search_Explosion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exponential_growth\">Exponential growth from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Great_Explosion\">The Great Explosion from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> The Jazz Explosion - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.discogs.com/composition/d1f12044-c434-4581-843e-de8359d50772-Pud-Wud\">Pud Wud</a>, live at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Chance\">The Chance</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poughkeepsie,_New_York\">Poughkeepsie, NY</a>, February 05, 1989, various clips, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video </li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Category:Allan_Holdsworth\" title=\"Category:Allan Holdsworth\">Allan Holdsworth</a>,  <a href=\"/Category:Stanley_Clarke\" title=\"Category:Stanley Clarke\">Stanley Clarke</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Randy_Brecker\" title=\"Category:Randy Brecker\">Randy Brecker</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bernard_Wright\">Bernard Wright</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Steve_Smith\" title=\"Category:Steve Smith\">Steve Smith</a></dd>\n<dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/p9ki_XgppHw?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Search_Explosion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Category:Edvard_Munch\" title=\"Category:Edvard Munch\">Edvard Munch</a> - One of several versions of the painting <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Scream\">The Scream</a> (or The Cry),  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Gallery_%28Norway%29\">National Gallery</a>, 1893, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oslo\">Oslo</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Norway\">Norway</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ibiblio.org/wm/paint/auth/munch/\">WebMuseum: Munch, Edvard</a> - Among theories advanced to account for the reddish sky in the background is the artist's memory of the effects of the powerful volcanic <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1883_eruption_of_Krakatoa\">eruption of Krakatoa</a>, which deeply tinted sunset skies red in parts of the Western hemisphere for months during 1883 and 1884, about a decade before Munch painted The Scream. This explanation has been disputed by scholars, who note that Munch was an expressive painter and was not primarily interested in literal renderings of what he had seen. </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56455\">Remember Leonid Liberman (author of LLCHESS)?</a> by <a href=\"/Dann_Corbit\" title=\"Dann Corbit\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 23, 2015</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=172464\">One mate to solve...</a> by <a href=\"/Leonid_Liberman\" title=\"Leonid Liberman\">Leonid</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 30, 2001</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301151036\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.078 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.619 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 92/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 204/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:1080-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301151035 and revision id 20014\n -->\n"
